# Solver binary tree — pulled at build time from the OpenRadioss
# release channel (see README.md for the recipe). 137-200 MB; would
# bloat the repo for no incremental value, and the AGPL distribution
# channel is upstream's own GitHub releases, not ours.
#
# Glob covers all release-asset variants the upstream channel
# publishes — _linuxa64 (ARM64 Linux, the one we use), _linux64
# (x86_64 Linux), _win64 — so a contributor accidentally pulling
# the wrong arch can't stage it either.
OpenRadioss/
OpenRadioss_*.zip
OpenRadioss_*.tar.gz
